~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : untag                                       ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : untag <username> <reason>

   This command is used to untag a certain user, removing his visible
   'tag' (namely a '?' before their name). 
   
   The reason string must be provided and is written to the users ulog
   so other adphins can look up why the user was un-tagged.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : tag, ulog
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
